# 👁️ OMNISCIENCE SECURITY MASK

# --- Credentials & Secrets ---
# NEVER commit these. They contain your Discord Token and RCON Passwords.
secret.txt
servers.json
*.cfg
!README.md

# --- Databases & Persistence ---
# This keeps your player rankings and match history private.
*.db
*.db-journal
*.sqlite

# --- Backups & Archives ---
# Prevents massive backup files from clogging your GitHub.
Backups/
*.tar.gz
*.zip
*.7z

# --- Python Environment ---
venv/
.env
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# --- OS & IDE Junk ---
.DS_Store
.thumbs
.db
desktop.ini
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- Logs ---
# Keep the clutter out of the repo.
*.log
alpha/
beta/
gamma/
delta/

